00:30:25.200 --> 00:30:31.420
But for the first time in all of humanity, God's saying, "Today's the day.

00:30:41.466 --> 00:30:41.768
There's a change coming.

00:30:41.768 --> 00:30:44.171
" It's like crossing over into another area.

00:30:44.171 --> 00:30:51.430
That's the only way I can tell you.

00:30:58.827 --> 00:30:59.120
The dispensation of grace will soon be coming to an end, and we're about to step over into the Tribulation.

