I have an anticipation, and I hope you do, too.

00:35:57.760 --> 00:35:58.159
I hope it comes across by me talking to you tonight.

00:35:58.159 --> 00:36:09.856
What I'm anticipating, a great harvest of souls is coming, ladies and gentlemen, beyond what you've ever seen before.

