And I believe that's what we're called to do.

00:37:07.564 --> 00:37:17.920
That's why He assembled us together for such a time as this.

00:37:46.987 --> 00:37:47.520
I don't believe it's by coincidence at all.

00:37:47.520 --> 00:37:54.560
I'm just telling you all, something major is about to take place.

00:37:54.560 --> 00:38:00.680
I've said it time and time again, but don't you feel that stirring?

00:38:00.680 --> 00:38:06.800
As I said last night, He told me, "This week marks something huge.

00:38:12.861 --> 00:38:14.494
" And as I heard Nearer, My God, to Thee playing by those trumpets and those horns and the violins, I sat there in awe that He chose us.

