He called each and every single one of us to be a great mouthpiece for Him in these last days.

00:38:43.236 --> 00:38:46.443
There's no one greater, there's no one too small.

00:38:46.443 --> 00:39:00.240
God will use every single one of us if we just have a yielded heart to Him and say, 'Here am I, Father.

00:39:00.240 --> 00:39:01.799
Send me.

00:39:01.799 --> 00:39:03.954
' I hope that encourages you.

00:39:03.954 --> 00:39:12.880
That part—I don't call it a program, this prayer service—those clips inspire me because I want to think big financially to get the gospel out big.

00:39:12.880 --> 00:39:14.630
You don't think small.

00:39:14.630 --> 00:39:23.440
If you think too small, it's just about 'my little church, my little friends, all this just to do what we've got to do.

00:39:23.440 --> 00:39:24.791
' No, you've got to think bigger.

