Stretch yourself.

00:39:25.387 --> 00:39:26.667
Stretch the way you believe.

00:39:26.667 --> 00:39:28.032
Stretch your capacity.

00:39:28.032 --> 00:39:30.620
Enlarge your tent today to think bigger today.

