And if God be for me, who can be against me?

00:45:06.800 --> 00:45:12.373
Regardless of what's being—even with a symptom like I have, you go, 'I don't care what the symptoms say.

00:45:12.373 --> 00:45:15.579
I'm not moved by what I see.

00:45:15.579 --> 00:45:19.510
I'm not moved by what I feel.

00:45:19.510 --> 00:45:22.259
I'm moved by what the word of God says.

00:45:22.259 --> 00:45:24.823
By His stripes, I am healed.

00:45:24.823 --> 00:45:31.706
' Even if my flesh doesn't totally agree with it right now, I'm not moved by what my flesh does.

00:45:31.706 --> 00:45:35.440
