' And I was whining about everything that I went through last week.

00:48:58.900 --> 00:48:59.230
He said, 'You sound like Elijah over there crying at the cave.

00:48:59.230 --> 00:49:01.840
' You know, 'Oh, everything's so bad.

00:49:01.840 --> 00:49:03.120
Jezebel's after me.

00:49:03.120 --> 00:49:10.880
' But He said, 'You haven't gone to the point of saying that you just want Me to take you home like he did.

00:49:10.880 --> 00:49:14.024
' He said, 'But Brandon, what you say out of your mouth is important.

00:49:14.024 --> 00:49:23.800
What you say out of your mouth is important, for life and death is in the power of your tongue, son.

00:49:23.800 --> 00:49:32.980
All that mealy-mouthed and all that stuff you're saying right now, watch what you're saying.

00:49:32.980 --> 00:49:38.480
' He said, 'I want to open your eyes to something.

00:49:38.480 --> 00:49:50.456
' And as I was interceding and feeling sorry for myself for the week that I had, He said, 'Give your angels something to work with right now, and I want to show you.

00:49:50.456 --> 00:50:02.800
' And I saw them fighting in the spirit realm, and I saw they had Captain America shields.

00:50:02.800 --> 00:50:11.529
These angels were fighting and they had Captain America shields—the round ones—and they had swords, and they were up there battling.

00:50:23.613 --> 00:50:23.866
And He said, 'Give them something to work with in the spirit realm.

00:50:23.866 --> 00:50:26.840
' And I said, 'Well, how do I do that?

00:50:26.840 --> 00:50:30.906
' He said, 'Quote the scripture concerning what you're going through.

00:50:30.906 --> 00:50:32.008
Quote the scripture.

00:50:32.008 --> 00:50:34.159
Use the sword of the Spirit.

00:50:34.159 --> 00:50:38.959
Quote the fiery word out of your mouth.

00:50:38.959 --> 00:50:42.925
Be a believing believer and not a doubter.

00:50:50.079 --> 00:50:51.599
You're an overcomer by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of your testimony.

00:50:51.599 --> 00:50:54.460
' Do you understand?

00:50:55.760 --> 00:50:57.344
You're not moved by what you see.

00:50:58.400 --> 00:51:02.479
You're not moved by what you feel.

00:51:02.479 --> 00:51:04.743
You're moved by what the word says.

00:51:04.743 --> 00:51:10.580
Now stand up and be who I've called you to be.

00:51:17.383 --> 00:51:22.331
You can either be mealy-mouthed, limp-wristed, and feel sorry for yourself, or you can be bold as a lion and say, "Thus far, Satan, and no further.

00:51:22.331 --> 00:51:23.200
" It is written.

00:51:23.200 --> 00:51:32.205
It is written, "Greater is he that is in me than he that is in the world.

00:51:32.205 --> 00:51:42.709
" It is written, "A thousand shall fall at my side and 10,000 at my right hand, but nothing shall come nigh me.

00:51:51.040 --> 00:51:51.958
" That's where you have to stand.

00:51:58.160 --> 00:52:12.309
And when the Lord showed me that, I felt when I started, I told Diana, I said, "Babe, go get that book that lady gave us, and quote those scriptures until we feel better.

00:52:12.319 --> 00:52:17.947
" She goes, "How many times are we going to read them?

00:52:17.947 --> 00:52:20.369
" I said, "Until we feel better.

00:52:21.619 --> 00:52:22.920
" The word will work if you work it.

00:52:22.920 --> 00:52:28.491
I said, "It don't matter how many times, hun.

00:52:28.491 --> 00:52:30.459
Even until we get tired.

00:52:30.459 --> 00:52:35.715
We quote these scriptures until they become real to us.

00:52:38.746 --> 00:52:41.643
" It becomes a Rhema word on the inside of you that is not just "Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star.

