Is that right?

00:53:25.839 --> 00:53:29.871
Some of you would fight it with all your heart.

00:53:41.839 --> 00:53:42.079
That devil tells you you're not saved.

00:53:42.079 --> 00:53:44.319
"Oh, I know I'm saved.

00:53:44.319 --> 00:53:45.859
How dare you?

00:53:45.859 --> 00:53:49.319
I'm born again by the blood of Jesus Christ.

00:53:49.319 --> 00:53:50.559
I'm born again.

00:53:50.559 --> 00:53:53.431
My name's written in the Lamb's Book of Life.

00:53:53.431 --> 00:53:55.564
Get out of here, devil.

00:53:55.564 --> 00:53:56.844
I know I'm saved.

00:53:56.844 --> 00:54:10.079
" But when he comes and tells you your son's not going to make it, your son's going to serve the devil, he has a plan—the devil has a plan for your son.

00:54:20.740 --> 00:54:21.010
"Oh, the devil's going to take your son.

00:54:21.010 --> 00:54:22.613
He's going to do witchcraft.

00:54:22.613 --> 00:54:23.580
He's going to do all...

00:54:34.160 --> 00:54:34.600
" The devil's got a plan for your son.

00:54:48.940 --> 00:54:53.177
You believe it because you don't realize that he said, "Train up a child in the way they should go, and when they get older, they'll not depart from it.

00:54:53.177 --> 00:55:02.240
" Regardless of how Johnny or whoever is acting right now, my God said that my children will be my offspring.

00:55:10.072 --> 00:55:10.256
The fruit of my offspring, the fruit of my children will be blessed.

00:55:10.256 --> 00:55:11.359
They're going to be blessed.

00:55:11.359 --> 00:55:13.670
They're going to be blessed coming in.

00:55:13.670 --> 00:55:15.470
They're going to be blessed coming out.

00:55:15.470 --> 00:55:16.937
My children will serve God.

00:55:16.937 --> 00:55:19.554
My children will be on fire for God.

00:55:19.554 --> 00:55:21.560
My children will not go to hell.

00:55:23.966 --> 00:55:24.297
And that's where you have to stand.

00:55:24.297 --> 00:55:32.319
Even when those kids are acting really bad, I'm training my child up in the way they should go.

00:55:32.319 --> 00:55:33.706
My kids know about Jesus.

00:55:33.938 --> 00:55:40.079
The seed of righteousness is inside of them, even if they're not displaying it right now.

00:55:40.079 --> 00:55:41.550
Now, I anoint them with oil.

00:55:41.550 --> 00:55:44.560
I anoint where they sleep.

00:55:44.560 --> 00:56:09.120
They may act rebellious in who they're hanging out with, and I might need to take a rod and spank their heinie a little bit because the Bible said if you spare the rod, you spoil the child.

00:56:11.839 --> 00:56:12.089
And it's not abuse; it's love.

00:56:12.089 --> 00:56:20.392
But either way, we're going to walk in love up in here.

00:56:23.829 --> 00:56:24.079
And love corrects.

00:56:24.079 --> 00:56:26.435
Love disciplines, not abuse.

00:56:26.435 --> 00:56:29.920
It didn't say beat them when you're angry.

00:56:29.920 --> 00:56:30.880
That's wrong.

00:56:33.119 --> 00:56:35.867
It's like I heard Kim Clement say, "If you're always chastising your kids, you're an idiot.

00:56:35.867 --> 00:56:36.756
" That's not smart.

00:56:36.756 --> 00:56:38.350
God doesn't chastise all the time.

00:56:38.350 --> 00:56:41.600
Always talking about God bringing judgment on things—God's not always judging and being mad.

00:56:41.600 --> 00:56:43.480
I'm going to be real with y'all.

00:56:43.480 --> 00:56:44.359
God's not angry.

00:56:44.359 --> 00:56:47.530
God's not up there always conspiring against you.

00:56:47.530 --> 00:56:51.840
You think he's, you know, "What is he doing today, Jesus?

00:56:51.840 --> 00:56:55.020
I think I'll slap him in the head with something.

00:56:55.020 --> 00:56:57.973
" I realize that God is a God of love.

00:56:57.973 --> 00:57:03.730
God is not conspiring up there thinking how he's going to make your life miserable.

00:57:03.730 --> 00:57:12.569
"Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:57:12.569 --> 00:57:16.559
" Above all things, everything for you to have a good and expected end.

00:57:16.559 --> 00:57:17.809
That's a good God.

00:57:17.809 --> 00:57:30.630
But most people think God's up there mad, and he's mad at America, boy, he's mad at Israel, he's mad at Thailand, he's mad at China, he's mad...

00:57:30.630 --> 00:57:32.140
No, God's not mad.

00:57:32.140 --> 00:57:38.630
Now, what does the Bible say?

00:57:38.640 --> 00:57:41.793
Seedtime and harvest never cease.

00:57:41.793 --> 00:57:45.680
Whatsoever a man sows, that will he also reap.

00:57:45.680 --> 00:57:49.324
Is that what the Bible says?

00:57:49.324 --> 00:57:53.644
As long as the earth remains, seedtime and harvest will always exist.

00:57:53.644 --> 00:58:01.245
As long as the earth remains, you can plant a seed in that ground.

00:58:02.137 --> 00:58:18.133
You can plant a seed in that ground, and if you water it and the sun hits it, it's going to grow.

00:58:19.456 --> 00:58:22.320
You can plant a seed in your wife, and you'll reap a baby.

00:58:24.260 --> 00:58:29.200
You can plant a seed in the church offering, and you're going to reap a harvest.

00:58:29.200 --> 00:58:33.531
Seedtime and harvest always work.

00:58:35.240 --> 00:58:35.440
I believe it.

00:58:35.440 --> 00:58:42.217
So because we live in a fallen world and you sow bad seed, you reap the harvest of that.

00:59:00.000 --> 00:59:00.280
So we are going to see, because seedtime and harvest is accelerated, the sowers and the reapers are going to go hand in hand like we've been told.

00:59:04.140 --> 00:59:06.380
And because of this acceleration, you're about to see seedtime and harvest like you've never seen it before.

00:59:11.154 --> 00:59:17.903
And when you see people sow to the flesh, they'll reap of the flesh, and when you sow to the spirit, they'll reap of the spirit.

00:59:17.903 --> 00:59:24.490
So, we're about to see things that you never thought you would see because time is short.

00:59:25.839 --> 00:59:28.606
And you're going to see things in the earth like you've never seen.

00:59:49.417 --> 00:59:55.120
You're going to see because the earth is crying out, the cup of sin is full, and the seedtime and harvest of that's full, and you're about to see tribulation for the seeds that were sown, and we've never seen anything like it before.

00:59:58.240 --> 01:00:01.857
The full manifestation of the seeds that were sown are going to be reaped all at one time.

01:00:03.680 --> 01:00:09.160
And God's wrath will be poured out upon this earth.

01:00:10.686 --> 01:00:17.119
And you're going to see it, and it's going to be like, "Oh my goodness.

01:00:17.119 --> 01:00:24.079
" That's what people—if you don't get born again, is what I'm going to say.

01:00:24.079 --> 01:00:33.280
But what we're also going to see is, I told you, great revival, great harvest, healings, demonstrations, manifestations of the glory right before the catching away of the church.

01:00:54.070 --> 01:00:54.700
I just believe it with all my heart.

01:00:54.700 --> 01:01:14.263
So, I hope you get excited about what we're about to see and have an anticipation for God to get even your neighbors saved, to get your daughters and your sons saved, to have revival in your homes, for husbands and wives to come together with great...

01:01:32.053 --> 01:01:32.319
"You know what, devil?

01:01:32.319 --> 01:01:38.160
We're going to punch you in the head today as a unit.

01:01:38.160 --> 01:01:40.506
We're going to be more in love.

01:01:40.506 --> 01:01:43.559
We're going to walk in love.

01:01:43.559 --> 01:01:48.827
We're going to have more friendship up in here.

01:01:48.827 --> 01:01:51.611
We're going to pray together.

01:01:51.611 --> 01:01:54.702
We're going to read the Bible together.

01:01:54.702 --> 01:02:01.794
And we're going to be more of a unit together than ever before.

01:02:10.199 --> 01:02:10.559
And we're not going to allow the devil to come in and rob our marriage through strife, through bitterness, through whatever.

01:02:12.862 --> 01:02:22.640
" The Lord told me, he said, "As the days approach, Brandon, you must make sure strife, if it ever exists, as a minimum, do not allow it in your home ever.

01:02:22.640 --> 01:02:27.280
Always diffuse it at all cost.

01:02:27.280 --> 01:02:29.430
It's not worth it.

01:02:29.430 --> 01:02:32.898
Make sure love is a pillar in your home.

01:02:32.898 --> 01:02:39.399
Do not allow strife in at all costs.

01:02:39.399 --> 01:02:42.400
It's not worth it.

01:02:42.400 --> 01:02:45.670
" So hopefully this helps you tonight.

01:02:45.670 --> 01:02:52.382
It's just stuff that we're dealing with, and that's what Diana and I talk about.

01:02:52.382 --> 01:03:05.858
It's what prepares us to make sure that we're walking in, and we have our t's crossed and our i's doted, and you're ready, and you have your eyes peeled.

01:03:05.858 --> 01:03:11.108
It's like talking to people, and they say, "I watch the crowd.

01:03:15.539 --> 01:03:17.451
I watch this.

01:03:17.451 --> 01:03:19.840
" Yes, I'm a people watcher, too.

01:03:30.169 --> 01:03:30.520
I hear them.

01:03:30.520 --> 01:03:32.880
I never let my guard down.

01:03:32.880 --> 01:03:34.125
Yes, I know.

01:03:34.125 --> 01:03:37.940
But we've got to have times of infilling and refreshing, too.

01:03:37.940 --> 01:03:59.942
We must have a time to drink from the Father and to make sure our cup is full of oil, our lamps are full, our lives are full and ready so that the enemy is not able to come and eat our lunch.

01:03:59.942 --> 01:04:06.259
He looks for the weak ones that are separated from the fold.

01:04:06.640 --> 01:04:07.780
The wolf does.

01:04:07.780 --> 01:04:16.109
Remember, the wolf is looking for the weak and sick ones.

01:04:16.109 --> 01:04:22.343
He doesn't go after the strong ones that have the full meat and are ready to fight.

01:04:22.343 --> 01:04:28.710
He looks for the ones that look like they're malnourished and off to the side of the fold.

01:04:28.710 --> 01:04:30.089
'Can I take him out?

01:04:35.450 --> 01:04:39.096
Can I take you out?

01:04:39.096 --> 01:04:40.826
' Does that make sense?

01:04:48.907 --> 01:04:49.413
You don't go after the strong ones; you go after the weak ones.

01:04:49.413 --> 01:04:52.399
So I want you to remain strong.

01:04:52.399 --> 01:05:03.564
I want you to remain strong and make this your best friend—the word of God in these last days.

01:05:21.760 --> 01:05:22.160
I even told certain folks I talked to, 'You must read Psalms 91 and Psalms 23 more and more and more.

01:05:22.160 --> 01:05:24.560
' You must know this.

01:05:24.560 --> 01:05:27.119
You must understand the power of communion.

01:05:27.119 --> 01:05:30.690
You must understand this: the meal that heals.

01:05:42.800 --> 01:05:43.280
It's so important, ladies and gentlemen.

01:05:43.280 --> 01:05:44.960
It's so important.

01:05:46.560 --> 01:06:02.010
I tell you this, and it's like I say all the time, if what you're doing is not working and you keep going down the same road all the time expecting different results, it's insanity.

01:06:02.010 --> 01:06:03.730
Try something new.

01:06:03.730 --> 01:06:19.039
That's why Diana and I, when we come to Megan and we do the therapies for Megan, if we didn't see results within the first 100 days because our budgets were limited, you don't keep doing the same thing expecting different results.

01:06:19.039 --> 01:06:22.079
After a point of time, you realize this isn't bearing any fruit.

01:06:26.251 --> 01:06:26.617
It's time to change directions.

01:06:26.617 --> 01:06:43.520
So if you don't have different fruit in your life after a while, and you don't see first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation—even a little bit of change with even coming and praying with me—then do something different.

01:06:46.240 --> 01:06:47.200
I do not want to be something that is a stumbling block for anybody.

01:06:47.200 --> 01:06:59.520
If you don't see change from praying with me and the things that I'm telling you, and it's not causing you to grow from glory to glory, then find something that does.

01:06:59.520 --> 01:07:04.079
Then find something that does, because we have to change from glory to glory.

01:07:05.760 --> 01:07:07.440
The word must change you from the inside out.

01:07:07.440 --> 01:07:14.120
If it is not, you're becoming stagnant and the enemy will devour you, especially with what I've seen coming.

01:07:20.800 --> 01:07:21.093
You must hear me.

01:07:21.093 --> 01:07:24.360
The Lord said, 'Remember, I was driving down...

01:07:24.360 --> 01:07:27.280
' I'll tell you where I was.

01:07:33.830 --> 01:07:34.160
I was on I-35 and Covell Road in Edmond, Oklahoma.

01:07:34.160 --> 01:07:37.540
You can look it up—I-35 and Covell Road.

01:07:55.302 --> 01:07:56.045
And there's a Starbucks there and a Braum's there.

01:07:56.045 --> 01:08:06.799
And there's a field over here with a Showtime Cinema Theater.

01:08:21.999 --> 01:08:22.319
I exited off that road.

01:08:23.600 --> 01:08:31.093
I took a right and I was going down the road to go to the post office.

01:08:41.164 --> 01:08:41.449
And the Lord spoke to me when I got off that road that day, and he said to me, 'Brandon, very sobering days are coming.

01:08:41.449 --> 01:08:44.160
Very sobering days are coming to the church.

01:08:44.160 --> 01:08:46.859
Sobering days are coming to the world.

01:08:46.859 --> 01:08:50.030
' And he said, 'But what's the opposite of sober?

01:08:50.030 --> 01:08:52.116
' And I said, 'Lord, drunk is.

01:08:52.116 --> 01:08:53.769
' And he said, 'Yes.

01:08:53.769 --> 01:08:58.951
Be being filled with the Holy Spirit to overflowing like a bubbling, bubbling, bubbling, bubbling.

01:08:58.951 --> 01:09:17.708
Let it be bubbling up out of you like a river of water coming up out of you by drinking of my spirit every day.

01:09:17.708 --> 01:09:19.920
Be being filled with the spirit every day.

01:09:19.920 --> 01:09:21.119
Brandon, don't get dry.

01:09:21.119 --> 01:09:21.839
Drink, Brandon.

01:09:21.839 --> 01:09:29.337
Be drunk in my spirit.

01:09:29.337 --> 01:09:31.782
Be filled with my spirit, for sobering days are coming.

01:09:31.782 --> 01:09:40.544
' And he said, 'Do you remember the scene in Mary Poppins, "I Love to Laugh," where Dick Van Dyke was floating on the ceiling?

01:09:40.544 --> 01:09:44.280
They were laughing and they were just having a good time.

01:09:44.280 --> 01:09:46.160
' He said they were laughing.

01:09:46.160 --> 01:09:48.400
He said, 'Learn to laugh more.

01:09:48.400 --> 01:09:49.750
Learn to laugh more.

01:09:49.750 --> 01:09:55.140
You're gonna have to learn how to laugh and have fun in life with the sobering times that are coming.

01:10:06.640 --> 01:10:12.684
Don't allow the things I show you prophetically to get down on the inside of you to the point where it changes you.

01:10:21.690 --> 01:10:22.040
You get filled with my spirit and pray out of the spirit, because when you see what I see, it has a tendency to get heavy.

01:10:22.040 --> 01:10:30.133
' Then some people say when I first start these streams, 'Brandon, you seem heavy.

01:10:30.133 --> 01:10:34.320
' Yeah, because I see the depth of the vision.

01:10:34.320 --> 01:10:40.239
I see things that I can't even allow myself to speak about upon this platform.

01:10:40.239 --> 01:10:55.480
There's things that you'll never know, never know, because I cannot allow that to be heard by the public because it would put people in danger.

01:10:55.480 --> 01:11:08.347
But the Lord has allowed me to say certain things to a certain individual now, and I'm thankful for that.

01:11:08.347 --> 01:11:16.719
But at the same time, the watchman gift is very heavy, some of these things.

01:11:16.719 --> 01:11:21.691
But you know what he said to combat it with?

01:11:21.691 --> 01:11:22.400
Laughter.

01:11:22.400 --> 01:11:24.320
Laughter in him.

01:11:24.320 --> 01:11:26.986
Be being filled with the spirit for what's coming.

01:11:26.986 --> 01:11:36.747
So I tell you all this so that you prepare yourself: be being filled with the spirit with laughter.

01:11:36.747 --> 01:11:42.995
Be happy, because a merry heart doeth good like a medicine, and a broken spirit dries the bones.

01:11:42.995 --> 01:11:44.983
A weary spirit dries the bones.

01:11:44.983 --> 01:11:46.853
A heavy spirit dries the bones.

01:11:58.057 --> 01:11:58.400
You need to be being filled with the Holy Spirit to the overflowing with laughter and joy in your households.

01:11:58.400 --> 01:12:12.690
How can you become happy and your wife follow you if you're always somber, like you've been eating dill pickles and you're sour, and you're going, 'Yeah, I'm heavy.

01:12:12.690 --> 01:12:15.045
I'm weary.

01:12:15.045 --> 01:12:18.354
I'm carrying the load.

01:12:18.354 --> 01:12:21.360
I've got the spiritual load on me today.

01:12:21.360 --> 01:12:24.175
I've seen so much.

01:12:24.175 --> 01:12:28.750
' How—what good is that?

01:12:28.750 --> 01:12:43.260
I started learning about the spirit of foreboding, walking around making sure it's not just me hearing things and, 'Oh, the devil said there's something, I hear there's something in the spirit realm that feels heavy all the time.

01:12:43.260 --> 01:12:45.060
' I feel that heaviness.

01:12:45.060 --> 01:12:54.160
Brother, you can walk around like that and it'll choke the life right out of you to the point where it's like, 'What am I even here for?

01:12:54.160 --> 01:12:57.031
There's such a heaviness in the atmosphere.

01:12:57.031 --> 01:13:02.914
' So you've got to check that and know the difference between a spirit of foreboding.

01:13:07.707 --> 01:13:07.973
A spirit of foreboding will choke the life out of you.

01:13:15.177 --> 01:13:15.451
It will make sure you always feel heavy, versus a call to prayer—a call to prayer.

01:13:15.451 --> 01:13:19.600
There's a big difference between a spirit of foreboding and a spirit of intercession.

01:13:19.600 --> 01:13:21.630
You'll have to look it up.

01:13:21.630 --> 01:13:23.886
A spirit of foreboding is terrible.

01:13:23.886 --> 01:13:30.903
And I used to walk around with that all the time—I'm talking the first ten years of my marriage.

01:13:30.903 --> 01:13:32.434
I'm always carrying this, Diana.

01:13:32.434 --> 01:13:39.627
And she goes, 'Man, I ain't never seen nobody like that.

01:13:39.627 --> 01:13:53.240
' Intercessory prayer—and she used to say this when we were first married—'Intercessory prayer on this side of it sucks, just being real, because it's heavy, Brandon, and I don't like this.

01:13:53.240 --> 01:13:55.440
' And I said, 'Well, I'm just doing my job.

01:13:55.440 --> 01:13:55.968
I'm sorry.

01:13:55.968 --> 01:13:59.320
I'm just doing my job.

01:13:59.320 --> 01:14:03.880
I'm just carrying the world, praying for the world.

01:14:03.880 --> 01:14:04.660
Just pray.

01:14:04.660 --> 01:14:06.453
Oh God, oh God, foreboding.

01:14:06.453 --> 01:14:13.307
' And then I realized one day the Lord said, 'My burden is easy and my yoke is light, son.

01:14:20.960 --> 01:14:21.147
I want you to have fun and enjoy life and have it more abundantly.

01:14:21.147 --> 01:14:33.153
' So I'm not trying to tell you all this—what I'm trying to tell you is I'm not trying to tell you to live underneath the umbrella when it's not storming; the sky is not falling.

01:14:33.153 --> 01:14:43.680
I want you to be being filled with love and joy and enjoy your life as I bring these things to you.

01:14:53.466 --> 01:14:53.715
I know it's heavy.

01:14:59.884 --> 01:15:00.196
I know it's heavy, and what we might see tonight could be heavy.

01:15:00.196 --> 01:15:07.199
But I'm taking the time to teach you a little bit before I just jump in the river.

01:15:19.679 --> 01:15:19.855
You have to be filled with joy.

01:15:19.855 --> 01:15:28.920
You have to be filled with hope, because God is a God of hope, and God is a God of peace, and God is a God of fun.

01:15:28.920 --> 01:15:51.180
He even said, 'Hey, the fun has just begun.

01:15:51.180 --> 01:16:10.400
' And he even said that last night.

01:16:10.400 --> 01:16:29.720
He said, 'Remember I told you the fun has just begun.

01:16:29.720 --> 01:17:06.263
As you're seeing all these things that are bad and I'm warning you of these things to pray about, the fun has just begun.

01:17:06.263 --> 01:17:11.720
' He's joyful.

01:17:11.720 --> 01:17:15.413
He's happy.

01:17:15.413 --> 01:17:23.510
He's not, 'Oh, Jesus.

01:17:23.520 --> 01:17:38.890
' I don't think Jesus ever has a sad day.

01:17:38.890 --> 01:17:39.880
Jesus doesn't.

01:17:39.880 --> 01:17:54.427
He's not up going, 'Well, you know, everything's going bad up here in heaven.

01:17:54.427 --> 01:18:01.795
' He's full of joy.

01:18:01.795 --> 01:18:23.240
Every single time I have a visitation, he's full of peace.

01:18:35.680 --> 01:18:35.947
He's full of love.

01:18:35.947 --> 01:18:40.800
His face—it's like one person asked me, 'What does it feel like?

01:18:40.800 --> 01:18:44.343
' I said, 'He's the lily of the valley.

01:18:44.343 --> 01:18:50.470
' He's the fairest of 10,000.

01:18:50.480 --> 01:19:15.480
There's nothing that can describe the majesty of who he is with this English vocabulary and what he has for you.

01:19:15.480 --> 01:19:21.966
He's altogether lovely.

01:19:25.199 --> 01:19:26.159
His fragrance is beyond human comprehension.

01:19:35.840 --> 01:19:39.760
Glory to God.

01:19:39.760 --> 01:20:06.739
So, did that help out at all?

01:20:06.739 --> 01:20:14.000
Maybe I helped somebody.

01:20:14.000 --> 01:20:29.573
Even if I helped one, I did something.

01:20:29.573 --> 01:20:57.599
Even if we helped one, I want you to live in victory.

01:20:57.599 --> 01:21:04.1000
I want you to live in joy in your homes.

01:21:04.1000 --> 01:21:08.630
I see the heaviness, y'all.

01:21:08.630 --> 01:21:30.400
I'm telling y'all, if anybody been up here telling you and be able to tell you the realness of this in the spirit realm is Brandon because I see the darkness and I never talk about it.

01:21:30.400 --> 01:21:32.700
I see the witchcraft.

01:21:32.700 --> 01:21:40.040
I see all the darkness go on, but I don't talk about it.

01:21:40.040 --> 01:21:43.760
I give you what I can enough to tell you.

01:21:51.120 --> 01:21:59.383
And the things I see outside of this are, oh God.

01:21:59.383 --> 01:22:05.040
And sometimes I try really hard not to carry that on to here.

